  <h1>5. Apply SEO Guidelines</h1>
  <p class="lead">Follow these requirements for every page to maximize search visibility.</p>

  <h2>Page Requirements</h2>
  <p>Every page on your site should include:</p>

  <table class="requirements">
    <thead>
      <tr>
        <th>Element</th>
        <th>Requirement</th>
      </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr>
        <td><strong>Content</strong></td>
        <td>Minimum 1000 words, unique and useful</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td><strong>Primary Keyword</strong></td>
        <td>One per page — in title, H1, URL, and first 100 words</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td><strong>External Links</strong></td>
        <td>Minimum 3 links to high-authority sites (.gov, .edu, major publications)</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td><strong>FAQ Section</strong></td>
        <td>5+ questions and answers with FAQPage schema</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td><strong>Footer</strong></td>
        <td>Embedded Google Map on every page</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td><strong>Schema Markup</strong></td>
        <td>Organization + FAQPage at minimum</td>
      </tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>

  <h2>URL Structure</h2>
  <p>For location-based businesses, use hierarchical URLs:</p>
  <pre><code>/state/city/service</code></pre>
  
  <p>Examples:</p>
  <ul>
    <li><code>/washington/seattle/weight-loss</code></li>
    <li><code>/texas/austin/emergency-dentist</code></li>
    <li><code>/california/los-angeles/teeth-whitening</code></li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Page Title Format</h2>
  <pre><code>Primary Keyword - Secondary Keyword | Brand Name</code></pre>
  <p>Keep under 60 characters. Put important keywords first.</p>

  <h2>Meta Description</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>150-160 characters</li>
    <li>Include primary keyword naturally</li>
    <li>Include a call-to-action</li>
    <li>Unique for every page</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Schema Markup</h2>
  <p>Include JSON-LD schema for:</p>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Organization</strong> — every site</li>
    <li><strong>LocalBusiness</strong> — for businesses with physical locations</li>
    <li><strong>FAQPage</strong> — every page (5+ Q&As)</li>
    <li><strong>BreadcrumbList</strong> — for navigation</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Pre-Launch Checklist</h2>
  <p>Before any page goes live:</p>
  <ul class="checklist">
    <li>☐ Keyword map documented</li>
    <li>☐ Unique title and meta description</li>
    <li>☐ H1 contains primary keyword</li>
    <li>☐ Primary keyword in first 100 words</li>
    <li>☐ 1000+ words of content</li>
    <li>☐ 3+ external links to authority sites</li>
    <li>☐ 5+ FAQ Q&As with schema</li>
    <li>☐ Images have alt text</li>
    <li>☐ Internal links to related pages</li>
    <li>☐ Google Map in footer</li>
    <li>☐ Schema markup validated</li>
    <li>☐ Mobile-friendly</li>
    <li>☐ Page speed optimized</li>
  </ul>

